<div class="col-12 text-center pt-sm-4">
<div><a href="https://www.vdb-loi.com/our_people/#our_partners" <i class="fas fa-th fa-2x text-vdbpurple"></i></a></div>
<div class="small text-center"><a class="text-vdbpurple" href="https://www.vdb-loi.com/our_people/#our_partners">GO BACK TO INDEX</a></div>
